node.text:
[#BeHomeNowSG —  Have a great month ahead, endure abit more and staying at home all day might be over soon 🤞🏻]
•
Along with some good news that selected food  and other services to resume operations on 12 May, let's hope for the best & stay positive! 😊
•
So what will you be cooking these few days to come? A simple yet filling meal that my dad cooked for the family was none other than the inspired "Din Tai Fung Style" fried rice 🤗
❗️Simply stir fry the rice with egg, salt, olive oil, soya sauce, grey prawn and topped with spring onion, and you're done! 😋🍽
